{"title_page": "Prosigk", "text_new": "{{Infobox German location\n|type = Stadtteil\n|Town = [[S\u00fcdliches Anhalt]]\n|image_photo       = \n|image_coa            = kein\n|coordinates       = {{coord|51|42|N|12|3|E|format=dms|display=inline,title}}\n|image_plan          = \n|state        = Sachsen-Anhalt\n|district         = Anhalt-Bitterfeld\n|elevation              = 81\n|area            = 15.08\n|population         = 752\n|Stand             = 2006-12-31\n|postal_code               = 06369\n|area_code           = 034978\n|licence               = ABI\n|website           = [http://www.suedliches-anhalt.de/ www.suedliches-anhalt.de]\n}}\n\n'''Prosigk''' is a village and a former municipality in the district of [[Anhalt-Bitterfeld]], in [[Saxony-Anhalt]], [[Germany]]. Prosigk is located 58.6&nbsp;km away from the closest city of Leipzig, and 152&nbsp;km away from its capital city in Berlin. It has an industrial and agricultural based economy and since 1 January 2010, has been incorporated into the town of [[S\u00fcdliches Anhalt]]. The village runs its own museum for the history of its fire brigade and several other services.{{citation needed|date=October 2019}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Villages in Saxony-Anhalt]]\n[[Category:Bezirk Halle]]\n\n\n{{AnhaltBitterfeld-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox German location\n|type = Stadtteil\n|Town = [[S\u00fcdliches Anhalt]]\n|image_photo       = \n|image_coa            = kein\n|coordinates       = {{coord|51|42|N|12|3|E|format=dms|display=inline,title}}\n|image_plan          = \n|state        = Sachsen-Anhalt\n|district         = Anhalt-Bitterfeld\n|elevation              = 81\n|area            = 15.08\n|population         = 752\n|Stand             = 2006-12-31\n|postal_code               = 06369\n|area_code           = 034978\n|licence               = ABI\n|website           = [http://www.suedliches-anhalt.de/ www.suedliches-anhalt.de]\n}}\n\n'''Prosigk''' is a village and a former municipality in the district of [[Anhalt-Bitterfeld]], in [[Saxony-Anhalt]], [[Germany]]. Prosigk is located 58.6 km away from the closest city of Leipzig, and 152 km away from its capital city in Berlin. It has an industrial and agricultural based economy and since 1 January 2010, has been incorporated into the town of [[S\u00fcdliches Anhalt]]. The village runs its own museum for the history of its fire brigade and several other services.{{cn|date=October 2019}}\n\n[[Category:Villages in Saxony-Anhalt]]\n[[Category:Bezirk Halle]]\n\n{{AnhaltBitterfeld-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200etop:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prosigk"}
